1
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,500
You have to understand, most of these people
are not ready to be unplugged.

2
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:08,800
And many of them are so inured, so hopelessly
dependent on the system...

3
00:04:12,100 --> 00:04:15,900
I know you're out there. I can feel you now.

4
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:20,200
I know that you're afraid.
You're afraid of us.

5
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:33,400
We've been trying to reach you, Detective.
Please, sit down.

6
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:38,700
I'm afraid I have some difficult news
about your partner.

7
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:26,100
The diner was empty except for the two of them.
Nobody saw a thing.

8
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:30,800
That's not possible. Someone always sees something.

9
00:22:44,300 --> 00:22:47,900
She left three months ago and never came back.
Her daughter still waits by the window every evening.

10
00:22:48,600 --> 00:22:52,400
Some people don't want to be found.

11
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:14,200
The letter arrived the morning after the funeral.
It was dated six weeks earlier.

12
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:18,900
He knew. He knew the whole time
and said nothing.

13
00:40:05,700 --> 00:40:09,500
I've been doing this job for twenty-two years
and I have never seen anything like it.

14
00:40:10,200 --> 00:40:13,800
Then maybe it's time you started
looking a little harder.

15
00:55:00,000 --> 00:55:04,200
Whatever happens next, I need you to know
I made this choice on my own.

